"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Yes, you heard it right….this technique even works for **Google, GitHub Student Dev Pack, AutoCAD Subscription & MS Office 365 Subscription** with the help of **EDU** mail ID.\\n\\n> EDU emails are used by colleges and university administrations. These emails are used for communication between the student, staff, and administration. They have an extension “.edu” instead of “**.com”**\\n\\n**1) Amazon**\\n\\n![6-month free trial for students](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*d0R3b4FSZYGaUeWfg5qcwg.jpeg)\\n\\nSign-up with ***[Prime](https://www.amazon.com/Amazon-Student/b?ie=UTF8&node=668781011)*** using your EDU mail so that you can access **six-month free unlimited movies and series**. After that you’ll automatically become eligible for the Amazon Prime student discount which entitles you to grab a membership for just **$6.49/month** instead of the original price $12.49/month.\\n\\nWhile using the Amazon Prime student discount, you’ll get **access to all Prime’s features including Prime Video, Prime Delivery** **etc.**\\n\\n## 2) [Microsoft Office 365](https://www.microsoft.com/en-in/education/products/office)\\n\\n![Office 365 free for students forever](https://miro.medium.com/max/1000/1\\\\*ZDRTXbtZxnFoeJnDxwituw.jpeg)\\n\\nAnyone with an EDU email can sign up to receive ***[Office 365](https://www.microsoft.com/en-in/education/products/office)***[ ](https://www.microsoft.com/en-in/education/products/office)**apps** for free. That means you’ll have access to **Outlook, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, OneNote, and Microsoft Teams**, as well as some **education-specific classroom tools** that aren’t available in the regular versions of Office 365. Users also get **1 TB of OneDrive storage space for free**.\\n\\n**Office 365 will be free** as long as you are eligible with a valid EDU mail address.\\n\\n## 3) [GitHub Student Developer Pack](https://education.github.com/pack)\\n\\n![Free pack of productivity tools for students](https://miro.medium.com/max/930/1\\\\*XjgaNmocCjDyA-OEFJoCaQ.jpeg)\\n\\n***[GitHub](https://education.github.com/pack)***[ ](https://education.github.com/pack)offers its Student Developer Pack to all students having an EDU mail. The pack includes a huge suite of **free and discounted tools** to help out coders and programmers including Canva, Digital Ocean, Microsoft Azure, Travis CI, MongoDB and more.\\n\\n*GitHub* *Student Developer Pack will be free* as long as your EDU mail is valid.\\n\\n## 4) [Google](https://workspace.google.com/signup/edu/welcome?hl=en)\\n\\n![Unlimited Google Drive free for students](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*9TKXNe87eSvEXm35otHAfQ.png)\\n\\nIf your EDU email address belongs to a school or college that uses ***[Google Workspace](https://workspace.google.com/signup/edu/welcome?hl=en)***, formerly known as G-Suite, you can grab yourself **an unlimited amount of storage on Google Drive for free**.\\n\\nIf you lose your EDU email address, you will lose access to unlimited storage plan and automatically return to the basic 15 GB plan. Your data will not be erased, but you must download it and get it below the 15 GB limit before you could upload new data.\\n\\n## 5) [AutoCAD](https://www.autodesk.com/education/edu-software/overview?sorting=featured&filters=individual)\\n\\n![Free access to AutoDesk tools for students and teachers](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*Ev8-KrF5-looZB9FrGO34g.jpeg)\\n\\n***[Autodesk](https://www.autodesk.com/education/edu-software/overview?sorting=featured&filters=individual)*** is the popular computer-aided design software, AutoCAD which let users create 2D & 3D drawings and is widely used in the architecture and engineering industries.\\n\\nStudents can **get access to Autodesk products and services** with an EDU email. AutoCAD software will remain **free** as long as you are eligible.\\n\\nOur blog is curated on topics related to **Personal Finance, How to Save Money, Tech Hacks & Expose Hidden Tips about Corporate Policies.**  If you’re interested and would like to hear more from us kindly **“Fund our Blog”** The more support we get, the more we produce informative blogs. Thanks for reading and supporting us.\\n\\n \\n\\n[crowdfund://0x656BAC46F5B28a5CE70a9b507e7b6bd8b685eA92?features=](crowdfund://0x656BAC46F5B28a5CE70a9b507e7b6bd8b685eA92?features=)\\n\\n**Follow “*[THE PANSOPHIST](https://medium.com/u/598c17b6e6e4?source=post_page-----df6bae667a43-----------------------------------)”* for more interesting stuffs like this.**\\n\\n**Follow “*[The Pansophist](https://www.facebook.com/Pansophist/)*” on Facebook.**\",\"timestamp\":1638460334,\"title\":\"How to Get Free Subscription from Amazon Prime & Other Apps\"},\"digest\":\"W4gBLwYlI7xLa2EPz_NP2APOoGKIHeSHk4qjIioazFo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x656BAC46F5B28a5CE70a9b507e7b6bd8b685eA92\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ORGZ8PWe0aQcrkz-9xClCq18wDQY1x1YFINCRxuiOs0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q_grVBDafiKZZ2mlrGV_3kPQNm3oMsbNAe72caJ7Urs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Z7-q0FWHUsjsLT5oDjeKmnX8T0omtpSZwGFxtnDqu8L8_thAh8kQC4zXuTOna6DtJM5usDgAnBm14yOwvnISzQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4bb029f701618d23f4aeaf71c8a7a2acdc62e6b956ae757d4bb11ac8f072037d58dc8a319ca3559923d7da2c4b3d67620fd0cbc9f3f92c0636d850ea414bffcb1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ORGZ8PWe0aQcrkz-9xClCq18wDQY1x1YFINCRxuiOs0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q_grVBDafiKZZ2mlrGV_3kPQNm3oMsbNAe72caJ7Urs\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"W4gBLwYlI7xLa2EPz_NP2APOoGKIHeSHk4qjIioazFo\"}"